            <table id="t08290006" tblwidth="pg-wide">
                <title>Master Disconnect Voltage Checks</title>
                <tgroup cols="3">
                    <colspec colname="1" colwidth="1.92in"/>
                    <colspec colname="2" colwidth="1.16in"/>
                    <colspec colname="4" colwidth="3.30in"/>
                    <spanspec namest="1" nameend="4" spanname="S1T6"/>
                    <tbody>
                        <row>
                            <entry colspan="3" spanname="S1T6">
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="BOLD">Master Disconnect Solenoid Voltage Check</emph>
                                </para>
                                <para>Check with key switch in on position and master disconnect solenoid removed.
                                </para>
                                <para>
                                    <hotlnk document="s08290_X08290001.xml" xrefid="x08290001">Bench test relay</hotlnk>
                                    . If relay fails bench test, replace relay and check for faults.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colname="1" align="center">
                                <para>Test Points</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="2" align="center">
                                <para>Spec.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="4" align="center">
                                <para>Comments</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colname="1">
                                <para>Master disconnect solenoid power lead to ground.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="2">
                                <para>12 &#177; 1.5 volts</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry colname="4">
                                <para>If voltage is missing, check for blown fuse F11 and check for open or short in
                                    circuits 16 RED 40 and A12A.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Master disconnect solenoid power lead to ground lead.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>12 &#177; 1.5 volts</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>If voltage is missing, check for open or short to high in circuit 16 WHT 40.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colspan="3" spanname="S1T6" align="center">
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="BOLD">Master Disconnect Switch Voltage Checks</emph>
                                </para>
                                <para>Check with key in on position and master disconnect relay installed.</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry align="center">
                                <para>Test Points</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry align="center">
                                <para>Spec.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry align="center">
                                <para>Comments</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Connector C5 cavity 2 to ground.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>12 &#177; 1.5 volts</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>If voltage is missing, check for blown fuse F11 and check for open or short in
                                    circuits 16 RED 40 and A12A.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Connector C5 cavity 2 to 3.</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>12 &#177; 1.5 volts</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <para>If voltage is missing, check for open or short to high in circuits 16 RED 40 and
                                    16 WHT 40.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                    </tbody>
                </tgroup>
            </table>
